{id:"item-alchemists-fire-flask",name:"Alchemist's fire (flask)",content:[{id:"Title",content:"Alchemist's fire (flask)"},{id:"StatGrid",content:[{title:"Category",content:"Adventuring Gear"},{title:"Cost",content:"50gp"},{title:"Weight",content:"1lb"},{title:"Type",content:"Standard Gear"}]},{id:"MultiText",content:["This sticky, adhesive fluid ignites when exposed to air.","As an action, you can throw this flask up to 20 feet, shattering it on impact. Make a ranged attack against a creature or object, treating the alchemist's fire as an improvised weapon.","On a hit, the target takes 1d4 fire damage at the start of each of its turns. A creature can end this damage by using its action to make a DC 10 Dexterity check to extinguish the flames."]}]}